Isang injection lang nito sa paligid ng mata,

00:25:39.110 --> 00:25:40.810
at ganap nitong sisirain
ang kanyang optic nerve

00:25:41.350 --> 00:25:44.500
wala pang limang minuto.

00:25:46.830 --> 00:25:48.700
Kakakuha ko lang kaninang hapon.

00:25:48.720 --> 00:25:49.810
Hindi ba perfect timing ito

00:25:49.830 --> 00:25:51.330
gamitin ito?

00:25:51.350 --> 00:25:53.570
Iyon ang tinatawag kong pagiging handa.

00:25:58.520 --> 00:25:59.330
Magwala ka!

